Download files from basespace to lab server using lab computer

# using the terminal
Move fastq files (fastq.gz), genome (.fa and .fai), and annotation file (gtf) to cluster using sftp or scp
Run FastQC on fastq files to check for quality of data
Index the genome, generate .idx files
Align data to indexed genome using Samtools, generate .bam files
Use bam files for all downstream analyses in R Studio

# using R Studio
Run Feature Counts pipeline, generate matrices to be used for deseq2
Run DESeq2 pipeline, generate normalized counts and DEGs
Run PCA plot pipeline
Run other analyses- bar plot, venn diagram,volcano plot, GO, HC, etc
# save environment for each analysis 
